        <abstract> 
<p>CD hopes Woodward was not the <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi> reviewer. "The manner in which he drags in immortality, &amp; sets the Priests at me … is base".</p> 
            <p>JDH has made CD feel he can "face a score of savage reviewers".</p> 
<p>H. C. Watson has written to him in tremendous praise of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
